OL,3,CCivil service to be 'ordered to cut
OL,4,C#2bn from budget'
OL,6,FThey will first be asked to reduce
OL,7,Fbudgets by 10% by 2028-29 in a bid to
OL,8,Fsave #1.5 billion a year, which the
OL,9,Fhead of the FDA union said equates to
OL,10,Fnearly 10% of the salary bill for the
OL,11,Fcivil service.
OL,13,FAdministrative budgets include HR,
OL,14,Fpolicy advice and office management
OL,15,Frather than frontline services.
OL,17,FDepartments will receive instructions
OL,18,Fin a letter from Chancellor of the
OL,19,FDuchy of Lancaster Pat McFadden in the
OL,20,Fcoming week, The Telegraph reported.
