OL,6,FA Cabinet Office source said: "To
OL,7,Fdeliver our Plan for Change we will
OL,8,Freshape the state so it is fit for the
OL,9,Ffuture. We cannot stick to business as
OL,10,Fusual.
OL,12,F"By cutting administrative costs we
OL,13,Fcan target resources at frontline
OL,14,Fservices ` with more teachers in
OL,15,Fclassrooms, extra hospital
OL,16,Fappointments and police back on the
OL,17,Fbeat."
