OL,3,CCivil service to be 'ordered to cut
OL,4,C#2bn from budget'
OL,6,FFDA general secretary Dave Penman said
OL,7,Fthe union welcomed a move away from
OL,8,F"crude headcount targets" but that the
OL,9,Fdistinction between the back office
OL,10,Fand front line is "artificial".
OL,12,F"Elected governments are free to
OL,13,Fdecide the size of the civil service
OL,14,Fthey want, but cuts of this scale and
OL,15,Fspeed will inevitably have an impact
OL,16,Fon what the civil service will be able
OL,17,Fto deliver for ministers and the
OL,18,Fcountry.
