OL,3,CCivil service to be 'ordered to cut
OL,4,C#2bn from budget'
OL,6,F"Whilst we welcome the move away from
OL,7,Fcrude headcount targets, the
OL,8,Fdistinction between back office and
OL,9,Ffront line is an artificial one.
OL,11,F"The budgets being cut will, for many
OL,12,Fdepartments, involve the majority of
OL,13,Ftheir staff and the #1.5 billion
OL,14,Fsavings mentioned equates to nearly
OL,15,F10% of the salary bill for the entire
OL,16,Fcivil service."
OL,18,FHe urged ministers to set out what
OL,19,Fareas of work they are prepared to
OL,20,Fstop as part of spending plans.
