OL,6,F"The idea that cuts of this scale can
OL,7,Fbe delivered by cutting HR and comms
OL,8,Fteams is for the birds.
OL,10,F"This plan will require ministers to
OL,11,Fbe honest with the public and their
OL,12,Fcivil servants about the impact this
OL,13,Fwill have on public services."
OL,15,FThe move comes after Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fvowed to reshape the "flabby" state
OL,17,Fand slash the cost of bureaucracy, and
OL,18,Fahead of the Chancellor's spring
